<li>Easy backup of your gmail account:&nbsp;<a href="http://gmvault.org/">gmvault</a></li>
<li>Edit text in PDFs for free: <a href="https://www.pdfescape.com/">pdfescape</a> </li>
<li>Some links suggested by students, thanks! <a href="https://datascienceprograms.com/learn/the-role-of-data-science-in-astronomy-and-interstellar-exploration/">1</a>, <a href="https://www.ucf.edu/online/engineering/news/five-stem-space-activities/">2</a>, <a href="https://californiadegrees.org/information-technology/masters-in-machine-learning/">3</a>, <a href="https://www.snappywords.com/knowledge/navigating-the-stars-a-young-learners-guide-to-astronomy">4</a></li>
</ul>
<p></p>
<ul>
<li>In case you&#8217;re wondering, I&#8217;m an <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.inter.it/" target="_blank">Inter</a> fan (and a bit of <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://www.wba.co.uk/" target="_blank">West Brom</a> from my time in the UK).</li>
</ul>
